{
  "stem": "20711.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they couldn't confiscate it when they came around.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my grandmother, who owned the car legally, showed them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Look it, you want that?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They turned away.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And because of being apart, the Russians didn't take it either.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He came up, and he was a fantastic mechanic, and he knew where the parts are.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he went to collect every piece of the car, and he put it together.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said to my father, I make a deal with you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I borrow your car.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I am going to use it for other purpose, which make money, and I will pay you a very good monthly fee for it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's how my father finally was able to put everything back into order because he received every month that payment.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And our friend used the car for transferring newspapers from the capital city of Budapest into the suburb because all our railroad stations and railroad were ruined in the war, and there was absolutely no transportation.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So a car was as valuable as-- as gold.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he made very good money with it, because he was also smuggling in a same time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He went to the Russian border.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He went to the Romanian border, delivering newspaper.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He picked up articles.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Like Russia had a lot of salt, so he would pick up bags of salt.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And on the way back, he brought back the salt and sold it in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Next time he was sent to the Austrian border, he picked up matches.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He picked up sugar or anything which the public needed and he would come back and sell that one.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So in no time, he became a rich man.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yes, he was also a Laszlo, which is a very popular Hungarian name, Mayer.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
